title: Ennis Gourmet Store Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, European, French, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Grocery store with cafe inside. Offers several veggie choices in  sandwiches and tapas, a few of which are vegan suitable. Owner is familiar with the vegan diet and could make a tapas plates for you - be sure to specify. Products are all local. The atmosphere is relaxed.
